 304}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800metre final\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"the lastOlympic Games\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she will be lining up with her in a GB vest after a meteoric rise in middle-distance running for the teenager.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994107866041888, \"rank\": 0.0005839913410453694, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a meteoric rise\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"middle-distance\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the teenager\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill was crowned British champion last month for the 800m after Hodgkinson, already guaranteed Olympic selection, opted to instead run the 400m at what doubled as the Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9962368793237674, \"rank\": 0.0037767470365600545, \"text\": \"British champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9743087041384182, \"rank\": 0.026368743040341047, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"already guaranteed Olympic selection\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on the eve of her Olympic debut, Gill said: \\\"Tokyo 2021 was such a memorable watch.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9989428349170955, \"rank\": 0.0010580441791899035, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"such a memorable watch\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed up until two in the morning to watch the 800s and watching Keely get that silver was unforgettable.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800s\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"that silver\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To think I am running on this stage is unbelievable.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait.\\\"\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill marked her national title by returning to her old primary school for work experience on the Monday morning.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"her national title\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"her old primary school\"